{"tid":346104,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺擦住個地下行路發出撻撻聲嘅人好似狗？","createTime":"2017-08-03T15:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T15:07:08.000Z","uid":470,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"539e2a1c76b20f981f20d82d4834a43897d69fc5","tid":346104,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"去啲好靜嘅地方見到呢類人真係好想打柒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母行路都唔撚識<br />\n行路都嘈鳩住哂<br />\n唔識遞起隻腳行？<br />\n<br />\n使唔使比對小學雞閃閃暴走鞋比你著？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲多數係肥仔/肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行步路都要慳力<br />\n<br />\n著皮底都算<br />\n著膠鞋波鞋/行地板果啲就仲仆街<br />\n吱吱聲勁刺耳<br />\n真係好想斬撚左佢地對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efc5881fc778d89183c7b115527ef1c61f33c2e","tid":346104,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b7ea317022e31088c4c01b49ba59ff5a94ce26","tid":346104,"uid":55990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b108027adf3059beed8c9384de1c9cf4e7023e78","tid":346104,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n利申行路無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613c90c5390eb385632e2bf3a05501ae2169b08b","tid":346104,"uid":84412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常都係臭西office女人</blockquote><br />\n有個同事唔洗望都知係佢行過<br />\n拖住咁行 嘈到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfb0d5a8def6a7f3460bb00755be15be3f103e1","tid":346104,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<br />\n利申行路無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></